title: Prison Songs (Vol. 1 & 2)
description: Here are both volumes of the prison Chain Gang and work songs which i downloaded off someone elses torrent. The second volume had the songs all wrong and i had a devil of a time fixing the titles. I had to go on amazon.com and listen to samples and match the songs by ear so i could correct the titles. Nonetheless,These are a must for any blues and historic music collector. I hope you enjoy them as much as i do. Also check out my other torrents which i mastered off vinyls.
